Codepen,is,a,browser,based,HTML,CSS,and,JavaScript,code,editor,that,supplies,an,instant,preview,of,what,is,being,programmed,Codepen,is,also,described,as,a,playground,for,front,end,developers,a,community,hub,and,forum,The,Codepen,API,can,be,used,to,access,stored,HTML,CSS,and,JavaScript,files,stored,on,HTTPS,endpoints,and,to,also,perform,auto,forking,In,order,to,fill,pens,with,different,values,developers,can,make,POST,requests,to,the,Codepen,endpoint,with,data,formatted,in,JSON,Using,this,prefill,editors,function,a,user,can,programmatically,update,their,project,titles,library,dependencies,CSS,colors,used,HTML,processing,and,more